Inept government cannot run health insurance better than companies. "The problem with the public option is that our government cannot run any program successfully." Investment Watch. August 18, 2009: "Social Security is broke, Medicare is broke, Medicaid is broke, the government is broke. And they want to run health care??? So we can look forward to another broke program with severe rationing of health care services."
